Name: Belly Dance Girl
About the game: These girls are really good professional belly dancers. They can dance in a very oily way and blow your mind away... Game Features: 1 - Nice and oily boobs 2 - Customized characters 3 - Each dancer has her own background music and it will produce music notes from top to bottom, you must press the note buttons below in a very good way to make sure the combo clicks count is not less than 100 and then after the girl has finished dancing you can own one ticket. 4 - Use the tickets to enter Fantasy Space or Dancer Studio to do more amazing things with those cute sweethearts... Enjoy yourselves!
